-- Spain's Applus+ to sell shares in institutional IPO
-- 
-- Wed Apr 02, 2014 02:31AM EDT
-- None



MADRID, April 2 (Reuters) - Spanish testing and inspection company Applus+ [IPO-AST.MC] said on Wednesday it would launch an initial public offering for institutional investors to raise 300 million euros ($413.83 million), mainly to pay off debt.

